name: Street lamp #1
description:
Part of the 'Experience' project, a digital experiment reflecting a work between photography, readings and lights using Flash in his prime; Now obsolete, it only remains lonely digital assets.

The themes tackled, touching to life; Human, Animal and Plant.
Through Itineraries, Errances and Fictions, feelings will take shape in an image tinged with bizarre and contrast, an instinctive atmosphere close to confession.

Photo taken in 2000 in the city of Valencia, Spain. Digitally manipulated.
